        <item>
            <title>【教学】帮 iPhone 清除 IG、FB 无用垃圾　实试释放手机 16 GB 储存容量</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/iphone-clear-cache-2024/tips-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-clear-cache-2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/iphone-clear-cache-2024/tips-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 11:30:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Facebook]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[instagram]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1254150</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>相信大部份读者每日也会上 Instagram、Facebook，小编自己也是 Instagram 重度成瘾者，经常会在 Instagram 和朋友互相传送迷因。长久下来，Instagram 和 Facebook 的 cache 会占用手提电话大量储存空间。此时就需要清理 Instagram 及 Facebook 的暂存数据。以下小编会利用 iOS 装置示范如何清除 Instagram、Facebook 的暂存数据，拿回本身属于你的储存空间。</p><p>如果你想查看你的 Instagram、Facebook 占用多少储存位置的话，可以进入「设定」，然后点击「一般」，选择「iPhone 储存空间」。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254163" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-2-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-2-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-2.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲进入设定</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254164" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_1-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_1-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_1.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「一般」</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254165" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_2-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_2-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_2.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「iPhone 储存空间」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254205" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-7-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-7-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-7.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲上下滑动，寻找你想知道占用多少空间的应用程式</p><p>在清理快取前，先看看小编 Instagram 和 Facebook 占用了多少储存空间。不检查犹自可，一看才发现这 2 个应用程式居然占用了近 17 GB 储存。此时我们可以按「删除 App」来移除应用程式，iPhone 就会清理应用程式占用的空间，之后再重新下载即可使用，无须重新登入。如果你的 Facebook 帐户连结了 Instagram，那么你登入其中一个社交平台后，系统就会自动帮你登入另一个。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254167" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-4-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-4-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-4.jpg 831w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲难以想像原来这两个应用程式占用了这么多空间</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254172" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-5-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-5-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-5.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲删除后重新安装 Instagram 及 Facebook</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254176" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_3-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_3-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_3-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_3.png 591w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲重新安装后，可发现之前的登入资料仍然存在。你不需再次登入，只要点击你的 Instagram 帐户即可</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254179" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_4-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_4-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_4.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Facebook 亦可以在你重新安装后，一键直接登入</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-6-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-6-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/photo_61499765565005-6.jpg 831w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲现在 2 个应用程式占用的空间大幅下降至约 100 MB ，节省了不少储存空间</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254193" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_5-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_5-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/apple_storage_5.jpg 831w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小编本来只有 87.52 GB 空间（红框示），重新安装 IG FB 后储存多了近 16 GB，<br />
提升至 103.37 GB（绿框示）</p><h2>总结：释放空间必备招式　不用再担心电话无位</h2><p>小编先前因为电话储存空间不足，所以才换了新电话，现在学懂这一招后，马上就腾空了不少储存空间。如果你的电话也有储存空间不足的问题，可以尝试删除 Facebook、Instagram 然后重新安装，这样应该可以腾空不少位置。不过要留意不是每一个应用程式删除后重新安装都可自动登入，小编试过删除 Telegram 后重新安装，Telegram 会要求小编自行重新登入，因此删除 Instagram 和 Facebook 以外的应用程式前，请先找个安全位置记下帐户密码等资讯，并确保你有方法再次登入该程式。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/08/how-to-use-gemini-on-ios-and-android-devices/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】iPhone 都用到 Gemini　教你如何在 Android 和 iOS 装置上使用</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/02/ios18-features-that-most-people-missed/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】iOS 18 大部分人可能错过的新功能　留言信箱广东话变文字 + 音量键电源键新操作动画</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/24/huawei-pura70-ultra-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Huawei Pura70 Ultra　由 iOS / Android 转会 HMS 不影响生活教学 + 实试</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/iphone-clear-cache-2024/tips-2/">【教学】帮 iPhone 清除 IG、FB 无用垃圾　实试释放手机 16 GB 储存容量</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
