        <item>
            <title>机管局手机特快行李托运服务启用，通过人脸识别、最快 45 秒完成整个程序</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/hkairport-phone-bagdrop-service/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hkairport-phone-bagdrop-service</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/hkairport-phone-bagdrop-service/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 06:23:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[国泰航空]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[机管局]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[香港快运]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1254058</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">机管局今日正式启用手机特快行李托运服务，即日起于国泰和香港快运两间航空公司提供服务，适用于 11 岁或以上持有电子旅游证件的旅客，包括护照、回乡卡、内地往来港澳通行证、签证等。机管局称服务过程最快 45 秒就可以完成，计划未来两年为 8 成的航空公司引入服务。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254067 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/airportnew24073118-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/airportnew24073118-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/airportnew24073118.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=570386">Now 新闻</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">机管局创新及数据分析总经理欧阳显宏表示旅客在手机的航空公司应用程式得到登机证后，便能在应用程式内完成手机特快行李托运服务的登记步骤。他提醒旅客的手机需具备近距离无线通讯技术的 NFC 功能，用作扫描电子旅游证件进行登记。登记步骤可在到达机场前完成，旅客需先扫描第一页的电子旅游证件，再将电子旅游证件拍向手机扫描便可完成登记。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254066 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1234-694x468.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="468" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1234-694x468.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1234.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=570386">Now 新闻</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">旅客完成登记并到达机场后，可直接前往附有手机特快行李托运标志的柜枱安放行李在输送带，按指示完成人脸识别核实身份和所属航班。电脑会自动打印行李标签，旅客将其绑在行李并使用手机扫描电子旅游证件和行李标签条码后即完成整个步骤。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254062 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kakaotalk_20240731_1-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kakaotalk_20240731_1-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kakaotalk_20240731_1-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254061 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kakaotalk_20240731_1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kakaotalk_20240731_1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kakaotalk_20240731_1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254063 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kakaotalk_20240731_1-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kakaotalk_20240731_1-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kakaotalk_20240731_1-2.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254065 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kakaotalk_20240731_1-4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kakaotalk_20240731_1-4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/kakaotalk_20240731_1-4.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.stheadline.com/society/3368912/%E6%A9%9F%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E6%8E%A8%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%89%B9%E5%BF%AB%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%8E%E8%A8%97%E9%81%8B%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99-45%E7%A7%92%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E8%A8%97%E9%81%8B%E7%84%A1%E9%9C%80%E5%89%8D%E5%BE%80%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E6%AB%83%E6%9E%B1">星岛</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">欧阳显宏补充因技术问题，于 2019 年 5 月 14 日或以前签发的香港特区护照不适用于此服务，需到入境处重新办理新护照。香港快运目前为所有旅客提供此服务，而国泰航空除了前往美国以外的旅客均可使用服务。要留意服务仅适用于免签证前往目的地的旅客，需要签证的旅客需要到传统柜枱办理手续。</p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.stheadline.com/society/3368912/%E6%A9%9F%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E6%8E%A8%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%89%B9%E5%BF%AB%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%8E%E8%A8%97%E9%81%8B%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99-45%E7%A7%92%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E8%A8%97%E9%81%8B%E7%84%A1%E9%9C%80%E5%89%8D%E5%BE%80%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E6%AB%83%E6%9E%B1">星岛</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1764051-20240731.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/25/hkexpress-seats-incident/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">HK Express 被指「怪兽家长」事主现身说法，事主：从来无抢过其他人座位</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/hkexpress-apology-to-chengs-but-still-no-full-explanation/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">调位事件苦主回港后收到 HK Express 道歉　「但快运仍未就事件作合理解释」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/18/cx-2/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">国泰就员工掟行李落楼梯致歉，网民反应两极：地勤无提供输送带</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/hkairport-phone-bagdrop-service/life-tech/travel/">机管局手机特快行李托运服务启用，通过人脸识别、最快 45 秒完成整个程序</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
